%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-brazil-x-ban-feud-content-moderation-free-speech-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeud%20with%20the%20Brazilian%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20The%20Financial%20Times%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F0baf2998-93da-4e94-968a-895853f5fea8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20was%20considered%20Yaccarino's%20right-hand%20man%20as%20she%20tried%20to%20attract%20advertisers%20back%20to%20the%20platform%20and%20boost%20the%20company's%20financial%20health%2C%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrazil's%20government%20banned%20the%20platform%20last%20week.%20It%20came%20after%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Alexandre%20de%20Moraes%20ordered%20the%20suspension%20of%20dozens%20of%20accounts%20that%20were%20said%20to%20be%20spreading%20disinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EX%20owner%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20then%20closed%20its%20Brazil%20offices%20and%20refused%20to%20comply%20with%20an%20order%20to%20name%20a%20legal%20representative%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20X%20post%20announcing%20his%20departure%2C%20Pickles%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20a%20privilege%20to%20lead%20the%20%40globalaffairs%20team%20and%20I%20leave%20with%20more%20memories%20and%20lifelong%20friendships%20than%20I%20ever%20expected%20when%20I%20first%20walked%20into%20the%20London%20office%20back%20in%202014.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile%2C%20the%20former%20X%20executive%20spent%20four%20years%20as%20a%20senior%20public%20policy%20manager%20in%20the%20UK%20before%20becoming%20the%20company's%20global%20senior%20strategist%20for%20public%20policy%20based%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20held%20the%20role%20of%20X's%20senior%20director%20of%20global%20public%20policy%20strategy%20for%20over%20two%20years%20and%20bec