r.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESteve%20Lewis%20has%20experience%20with%20both%2015-%20and%2030-year%20mortgages%20%E2%80%94%20and%20if%20he%20buys%20more%20investment%20properties%20in%20the%20future%2C%20he%20says%20he'd%20pick%20the%20shorter-term%20loan%20every%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20very%20first%20property%20he%20bought%20%E2%80%94%20a%20condo%20in%20New%20Jersey%20%E2%80%94%20was%20his%20primary%20residence%20for%2014%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20property%20was%20already%20under%20a%2030-year%2C%20so%20I%20just%20left%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Lewis%2C%20who%20works%20in%20cybersecurity%20full-time%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20In%202014%2C%20he%20purchased%20and%20moved%20into%20a%20single-family%20home.%20Rather%20than%20sell%20the%20condo%2C%20he%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20rental.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20his%20next%20two%20investment-specific%20properties%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20went%20to%20the%2015-year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20really%20good%20decision%20at%20that%20time%20and%20what%20I%20recommend%20to%20anyone%20that's%20going%20to%20venture%20out%20into%20this%20kind%20of%20investment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fsteve~lewis_15-vs-30-year-mortgage-which-one-is-the-activity-7232703127861227520-MQYl%2F%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprefers%20the%20shorter-term%20loan%20for%20a%20few%20reasons%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20main%20one%20being%20that%20it%20allows%20you%20to%20build%20equity%20much%20quicker.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20owning%20a%20property%20for%20just%20five%20years%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20third%20of%20the%20property%20is%20paid%20off%20already%20by%20your%20tenants%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Lewis%2C%20who%20sold%20his%20three%20condos%20in%202024%20and%20plans%20to%20use%20the%20cash%20to%20invest%20in%20commercial%20real%20estate.%20BI%20verified%20the%20three%20sales%20by%20reviewing%20his%20settlement%20statements.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhereas%2C%20with%20a%2030-year%20mortgage%2C%20%26quot%3Byou're%20paying%20mostly%20interest%20for%20your%20first%20seven%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20trade-off%20is%20cash%20flow%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%2C%20but%20that's%20never%20been%20his%20primary%20focus%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20always%20a%20debate%20between%20cash%20flow%20or%20equity%20building.%20If%20you%20take%20a%2030-year%2C%20your%20payment%20will%20be%20lower%2C%20so%20you'll%20have%20more%20cash%20flow.%20If%20you%20do%20a%2015-year%20mortgage%2C%20your%20payment%20will%20be%20higher%2C%20but%20your%20equity%20will%20build%20much%20quicker.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe'd%20rather%20sacrifice%20some%20cash%20flow%20to%20get%20a%20bigger%20payday%20at%20the%20closing%20table.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20really%2C%20really%20nervous%20about%20cash%20flow%2C%20do%20your%2030-year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20recommend%20doing%20a%2015-year%20and%2020%25%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20with%20a%20higher%20monthly%20payment%2C%20Lewis%20said%20he%20was%20able%20to%20profit%20between%20%24100%20and%20%24150%20a%20month%20on%20both%20of%20his%2015-year-mortgage%20condos.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20thinks%20that%20going%20with%20a%20shorter%20loan%20forced%20him%20to%20make%20a%20better%20decision%20when%20selecting%20his%20investment%20property.%20After%20all%2C%20when%20calculating%20cash%20flow%20(income%20minus%20expenses)%2C%20it's%20harder%20to%20make%20the%20numbers%20work%20when%20you%20have%20a%20bigger%20mortgage%20payment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20go%20the%2015-year%20route%2C%20Lewis%2