0Comparisons%20on%20social%20media%20are%20linked%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftransformation-instagram-photos-negative-body-image-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eincreased%20negative%20self-talk%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20feeling%20worse%20about%20yourself.%20With%20a%20total%20cut-off%20from%20Instagram%2C%20my%20mental%20health%20improved%20because%20I%20wasn't%20thinking%20about%20how%20someone%20else%20was%20superficially%20better%20off%20than%20me.%20Since%20quitting%20the%20app%2C%20I%20felt%20more%20secure%20in%20myself%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20happier%20and%20less%20anxious.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237cf99fa-b490-496b-9429-99e5d6855c78%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20asked%20my%20friends%20to%20text%20me%20more%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20soon%20became%20evident%20that%20I%20had%20no%20access%20to%20memes%2C%20sending%20fluttering%20hearts%20on%20friends'%20stories%2C%20or%20finding%20out%20about%20the%20new%20bougie%20restaurant%20in%20town.%20This%20felt%20like%20a%20hard%20trade-off%20because%20I%20like%20having%20meme-only%20conversations%20with%20certain%20friends%2C%20and%20who%20doesn't%20love%20a%20good%20laugh%20or%20tutorial%3F%20But%20that%20was%20the%20price%20I%20had%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20also%20didn't%20want%20to%20miss%20out%20on%20my%20close%20friends%20and%20family's%20important%20moments.%20So%2C%20I%20requested%20them%20to%20share%20pictures%20from%20their%20trips%20or%20life%20events%20by%20text%2C%20and%20so%20would%20I.%20Everyone%20agreed.%20This%20exercise%20also%20helped%20me%20realize%20that%20I%20needed%20new%20ways%20to%20stay%20connected%20with%20people%20I%20care%20about%2C%20so%20I%20started%20texting%20and%20calling%20them%20more.%20It%20took%20more%20time%20than%20DMing%20but%20we%20were%20having%20deeper%20conversations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2252afc269-b2da-4328-a107-38b23e08c4f9%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20play%20games%20now%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithout%20Instagram%2C%20my%20phone%20lost%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20purpose%2C%20especially%20with%20all%20my%20work%20and%20text%20apps%20on%20my%20laptop.%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20do%20during%20my%20downtime.%20So%2C%20I%20doubled%20down%20on%20games.%20I've%20always%20been%20a%20crossword%20solver%20and%20added%20more%20games%20to%20my%20phone%20like%20Connections%2C%20Wordle%2C%20and%20LinkedIn%20games.%20Overall%2C%20they%20take%20less%20than%2030%20minutes%20to%20finish%2C%20but%20it's%20enough%20of%20a%20dopamine%20hit%20when%20I'm%20looking%20to%20do%20something%20on%20my%20phone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20had%20urges%20to%20redownload%20Instagram%2C%20mostly%20during%20vacations%20when%20I'm%20surrounded%20by%20beautiful%20views%2C%20gorging%20on%20Instagrammable%20food%2C%20and%20taking%20pictures%20with%20my%20loved%20ones.%20But%20I%20stop%20myself%20because%20the%20pros%20far%20outweigh%20these%20fleeting%20seconds%20of%20validation%20and%20maybe%20even%20showing%20off.%20I%20still%20document%20things%20and%20save%20them%20on%20my%20phone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20initial%20days%2C%20I%20suspected%20that%20people%20not%20in%20touch%20with%20me%20would%20think%20I%20had%20zero%20life.%20But%20I've%20made%20my%20peace%20with%20it%20and%20feel%20relaxed%20that%20I%20have%20nothing%20to%20prove%20to%20anyone.%20Being%20off%20Instagram%20has%20helped%20me%20feel%20more%20secure%2C%20gain%20tons%20of%20time%20for%20work%2C%20and%20build%20deeper%20connections%20with%20friends.%20Maybe%20I%20will%20go%20back%20one%20day%2C%20but%20for%20now%2C%20these%20benefits%20are%20worth%20more%20than%20an%20app%20to%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeleted-instagram-and-its-helped-anxiety-fomo-produ