%3B%20one%20analyst%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20can%20also%20generate%20revenue%20through%20AI%20chatbots%20like%20Gemini.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20announced%20last%20week%20it%20would%20reinstate%20its%20Gemini%20AI%20chatbot's%20ability%20to%20generate%20pictures%20of%20people%20after%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-gemini-ai-pause-image-generation-people-woke-complaints-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaused%20the%20feature%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20several%20months%20due%20to%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20sprinkled%20in%20some%20other%20long-promised%20features%2C%20such%20as%20letting%20users%20customize%20their%20own%20chatbots.%20However%2C%20there's%20just%20one%20catch%3A%20you'll%20need%20to%20pay%20Google%20%2419.99%20a%20month%20to%20use%20these%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20is%20certainly%20not%20the%20only%20company%20that's%20discovered%20that%20the%20AI%20boom%20brings%20a%20new%20way%20for%20customers%20to%20pay%20money%20for%20these%20features%2C%20but%20for%20Alphabet%2C%20it%20opens%20up%20even%20bigger%20potential%20in%20a%20growing%20new%20section%20of%20its%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwenty%20years%20after%20Google%20became%20a%20publicly%20traded%20company%2C%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20its%20revenue%20still%20comes%20from%20search%20advertising.%20In%20recent%20months%20though%2C%20the%20search%20giant%20has%20dropped%20several%20hints%20that%20subscriptions%20are%20becoming%20an%20increasingly%20important%20part%20of%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20Alphabet%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20said%20paid%20subscriptions%20were%20generating%20%2415%20billion%20of%20annual%20revenue%20%E2%80%94%20up%20five%20times%20since%202019%20%E2%80%94%20most%20of%20which%20came%20from%20YouTube%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%20three%20quarters%2C%20revenue%20growth%20of%20Google's%20%26quot%3Bsubscriptions%2C%20platforms%2C%20and%20devices%26quot%3B%20segment%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20known%20a%20year%20ago%20simply%20as%20%26quot%3BGoogle%20Other%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20has%20outpaced%20Search%20growth%2C%20per%20Business%20Insider's%20analysis.%20The%20subscriptions%20segment%20includes%20the%20company's%20various%20YouTube%20subscriptions%20%E2%80%94%20Music%2C%20TV%2C%20Premium%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20Google%20One%20service.%20It%20also%20includes%20Pixel%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Google%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment%20for%20this%20story%20but%20pointed%20to%20the%20company's%20Q2%20earnings%20call%2C%20where%20Alphabet%20president%20Ruth%20Porat%20noted%20that%20the%20company's%20subscription%20business%20%26quot%3Bdrives%20the%20majority%20of%20revenue%20growth%26quot%3B%20in%20this%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESearch%20advertising%20is%20a%20volatile%20business%20(and%20for%20Google%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-artificially-raised-ad-prices-could-cost-it-100-billion-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20that's%20under%20regulatory%20threat%3C%2Fa%3E).%20That's%20why%20Wall%20Street%20wants%20to%20see%20if%20the%20company%20can%20grow%20subscription%20revenue%20as%20a%20more%20reliable%20business%2C%20says%20Dan%20Morgan%2C%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Synovus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20advantageous%20to%20build%20a%20bigger%20subscription%20base%20to%20even%20out%20some%20of%20the%20ebbs%20and%20flows%20from%20search%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20He%20said%20that%20while%20Wall%20Street%20gets%20excited%20about%20Google%20Cloud's%20growth%20from%20AI%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20don't%20talk%20much%20about%20YouTube%20Premium%20going%20up.%20It's%20a%20sizable%20number.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20parts%20of%20the%20business%20that%20have%20grown%20more%20robust%2C%20like%20Cloud%20and%20YouTube%2C%20Google%20breaks%20out%20their%20revenue%20when%20reporting%20earnings.%20Investors%20would%20undoubtedly%20love%20a%20better%20idea%20of%20how%20much%20revenue%20subscriptions%20generate%20in%20total.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20caveat%20that%20Google's%20subscriptions%20are%20entangled%20with%20other%20revenues%2C%20Morgan%20estimated%20that%20Google's%20subscription%20takings%20trend%20a%20little%20over%2010%25%20of%20its%20total%20revenues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20could%20become%20an%20Apple-like%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a55f819-e8c1-48d3-b778-35d51f542245%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Apple%20effect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20been%20hugely%20successful%20at%20subscriptions.%20Last%20year%20the%20company%20announced%20it%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-earnings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1%20billion%20subscribers%3C%2Fa%3E%20paying%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bservices%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20group%20of%20subscriptions%20that%20includes%20Apple%20TV%2B%2C%20Apple%20Music%2C%20and%20iCloud%20storage.%20In%202023%2C%2022%25%20of%20its%20net%20sales%20came%20from%20this%20%26quot%3Bservices%26quot%3B%20segment%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20percentage%20of%20App%20Store%20sales%20Apple%20takes%20for%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20consumer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcirpapple.substack.com%2Fp%2Ficloud-storage-remains-apples-most%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%20by%20Consumer%20Intelligence%20Research%20Partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20paid%20iCloud%20storage%20was%20the%20most%20popular%20Apple%20service%20used%20by%20its%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223089%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tim%20Cook.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6669f3feed9a404d829d1819%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222190%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook.%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20similar%20tactic%20Google%20takes%20with%20its%20storage%20subscription.%20Before%2C%20it%20offered%20generous%20amounts%20of%20free%20cloud%20storage%20to%20users.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20amount%20of%20free%20allocated%20storage%20shrunk%20as%20Google%20nudged%20users%20to%20pay%20for%20its%20Google%20One%20subscription%2C%20which%20allows%20them%20more%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Estorage%20for%20photos%2C%20emails%2C%20and%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20to%20be%20working%20for%20Google%2C%20too%3A%20In%20February%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fsundarpichai%2Fstatus%2F1755988540037730738%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPichai%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20company%20had%20crossed%20100%20million%20Google%20One%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c6c4f1b-aa69-47f8-b309-ca562146d49f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20AI%20opportunity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECrossing%20that%20100%20million%20threshold%20coincided%20with%20Google%20bundling%20its%20new%20Gemini%20Advanced%20service%20into%20Google%20One%E2%80%94a%20clever%20way%20to%20get%20users%20hooked%20on%20a%20new%20technology%20the%20company%20is%20investing%20heavily%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20users%20have%20been%20conditioned%20to%20expect%20some%20level%20of%20free%20service%20from%20Google.%20The%20company%20lets%20anyone%20use%20the%20basic%20version%20of%20its%20Gemini%20chatbot%20and%20developer%20tools%20free%20of%20charge%2C%20but%20it%20keeps%20more%20capable%20models%20and%20advanced%20features%2C%20such%20as%20image%20generation%2C%20behind%20a%20paywall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBernstein%20senior%20analyst%20Mark%20Shmulik%20compared%20this%20tactic%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F50-of-all-cds-had-aol-stamped-on-them-during-aols-prime-2010-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAOL's%20CD%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20the%20company%20mass-distributed%20CDs%20that%20gave%20users%20a%20free%20trial%2