%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%2C%20while%20her%20husband%20systematically%20filmed%20the%20suspected%20rapes%20and%20stored%20thousands%20of%20images%20as%20well%20as%20videos%20later%20found%20by%20the%20investigators.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CI%20was%20sacrificed%20on%20the%20altar%20of%20vice...%20They%20regarded%20me%20like%20a%20rag%20doll%2C%20like%20a%20garbage%20bag...%20I%20no%20longer%20have%20an%20identity.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20will%20ever%20rebuild%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20testified%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ffrance-wife-rape-trial-gisele-dominique-pelicot-b2607529.html%5C%22%3EThe%20Independent%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnShe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20me%2C%20everything%20collapses.%20These%20are%20scenes%20of%20barbarity%2C%20of%20rape.%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnShe%20said%20she%20was%20abused%20at%20least%20six%20times%20by%20someone%2C%20who%20was%20known%20to%20have%20HIV.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CMy%20life%20was%20in%20danger%20but%20not%20one%20second%20did%20anyone%20stop...%20I%20was%20tested%20for%20HIV%20as%20one%20man%20who%20came%20(to%20rape%20me)%20six%20times%20was%20seropositive%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gisele%20told%20the%20court%2C%20testifying%20about%20the%20abuse%20inflicted%20on%20her%20between%202011%20and%202020%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F09%2F05%2Fworld-news%2Ffrench-husband-accused-of-drugging-wife-allegedly-let-hiv-positive-attacker-rape-her-six-times%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EPolice%20'saved%20my%20life'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20woman%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpolice%20saved%20my%20life%E2%80%9D%20after%20they%20investigated%20her%20husband's%20computer%20back%20in%20November%202020%20after%20he%20was%20caught%20by%20a%20security%20guard%20filming%20up%20the%20skirts%20of%20women%20at%20a%20supermarket%20near%20their%20home%20in%20a%20village%20in%20southern%20France%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Farticle%2F2024%2Fsep%2F05%2Ffrench-woman-world-fell-apart-alleged-rapes-men-invited-by-husband-gisele-pelicot%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDescribing%20the%20moment%20the%20investigators%20first%20showed%20her%20the%20videos%20of%20images%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20orchestrated%20and%20filmed%20by%20her%20husband%2C%20Gisele%20Pelicot%20termed%20it%20as%20%E2%80%9Can%20explosion%2C%20a%20tsunami%E2%80%9D.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CMy%20world%20is%20falling%20apart.%20For%20me%2C%20everything%20is%20falling%20apart.%20Everything%20I%20have%20built%20up%20over%2050%20years...%20Frankly%2C%20these%20are%20scenes%20of%20horror%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20while%20Dominique%20Pelicot%20kept%20listening%20to%20her%20in%20court%20with%20his%20head%20bowed.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20report%20stated%20that%20while%20investigating%20the%20case%2C%20police%20saw%20a%20file%2C%20labelled%20%26quot%3Babuses%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20USB%20drive%20that%20was%20connected%20to%20Dominique%20Pelicot's%20computer.%20While%20searching%20the%20drive%2C%20officials%20found%20nearly%2020%2C000%20images%20and%20films%20of%20the%20woman%20getting%20raped%20almost%20100%20times.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EThe%20crime%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20police%2C%20the%20accused%20husband%20used%20to%20crush%20sleeping%20pills%20and%20anti-anxiety%20medication%20and%20mix%20them%20into%20his%20wife's%20meal%20or%20wine.%20He%20then%20used%20to%20invite%20men%20to%20rape%20her%20after%20contacting%20them%20through%20an%20online%20chatroom.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnDominique%20Pelicot%20as%20well%20as%2050%20other%20men%2C%20aged%20between%2026%20and%2074%2C%20are%20on%20trial%2C%20reports%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22htt