lockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%2C%20co-produced%20by%20Kangana's%20Manikarnika%20Films%20and%20Zee%20Studios%2C%20was%20initially%20set%20to%20release%20on%20September%206.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20censor%20certificate%2C%20Zee%20Entertainment%20Enterprises%20took%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%2C%20seeking%20intervention%20to%20clear%20the%20film%20for%20release.%20This%20legal%20battle%20has%20led%20to%20further%20delays%2C%20and%20with%20no%20favourable%20outcome%20from%20the%20court%2C%20the%20release%20is%20now%20indefinitely%20postponed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20had%20refused%20to%20grant%20any%20urgent%20relief%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20directive%20issued%20by%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20directing%20the%20censor%20board%20to%20consider%20objections%20to%20the%20movie%20before%20certifying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20The%20Film%20About%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20is%20based%20on%20the%20Emergency%20declared%20by%20former%20prime%20minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20in%201975%2C%20a%20controversial%2021-month%20period%20often%20regarded%20as%20one%20of%20the%20darkest%20chapters%20in%20Indian%20democracy.%20Ms%20Ranaut%20plays%20the%20role%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20the%20movie%20delves%20into%20key%20historical%20events%2C%20including%20the%20Emergency%20itself%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20assassination%2C%20and%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20Khalistan%20movement%20under%20Jarnail%20Singh%20Bhindranwale%20in%20the%201980s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ensemble%20cast%20features%20veteran%20actors%20such%20as%20Anupam%20Kher%2C%20Shreyas%20Talpade%2C%20and%20Milind%20Soman.%20The%20screenplay%20has%20been%20written%20by%20Ranaut%2C%20further%20marking%20her%20growing%20influence%20as%20a%20filmmaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20movie%20was%20initially%20planned%20for%20a%20release%20last%20year%2C%20various%20delays%20-%20including%20the%20scheduling%20around%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20-%20pushed%20the%20release%20first%20to%20June%202024%20and%20then%20to%20September.%20The%20ongoing%20certification%20issues%20with%20the%20CBFC%20have%20left%20the%20future%20release%20date%20uncertain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Are%20The%20Objections%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movie%20has%20faced%20backlash%2C%20particularly%20from%20the%20Sikh%20community.%20The%20Shiromani%20Gurdwara%20Parbandhak%20Committee%20(SGPC)%2C%20the%20highest%20body%20responsible%20for%20managing%20Sikh%20religious%20institutions%2C%20has%20raised%20concerns%20that%20the%20film%20distorts%20historical%20facts%20and%20misrepresents%20the%20Sikh%20community.%20Following%20the%20release%20of%20the%20trailer%2C%20the%20SGPC%2C%20alongside%20the%20Akal%20Takht%2C%20demanded%20an%20immediate%20ban%20on%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20legal%20notice%20was%20issued%20by%20the%20SGPC%20to%20the%20producers%2C%20alleging%20that%20certain%20scenes%20in%20the%20trailer%20were%20%26quot%3Banti-Sikh%26quot%3B%20and%20hurt%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20community.%20The%20SGPC%20has%20since%20reached%20out%20to%20both%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20and%20the%20CBFC%20to%20seek%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725608400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F84enior8_kangana-ranaut-emergency_625x300_02_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstill-waiting-for-kangana-ranaut-says-release-of-emergency-postponed-6502742%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kangana%20Ranaut's%20film%20'Emergency'%20has%20been%20postponed%20yet%20again%2C%20following%20opposition%20from%20Sikh%20organisations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstill-waiting-for-kangana-ranaut-says-release-of-emergency