%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fhe-begged-everyone-saying-his-wife-was-pregnant-renukaswamys-father-wants-accused-to-be-punished-the-way-his-son-was-tortured%2Farticleshow%2F113117849.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Massive%20Boost%20In%20Sustainable%20Energy%20Spending%20By%20Government%3A%20Pralhad%20Joshi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPralhad%20Joshi%2C%20Minister%20of%20New%20and%20Renewable%20Energy%2C%20today%20said%20that%20the%20Centre%20has%20spent%20significantly%20on%20sustainable%20energy%20for%20a%20greener%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20India%20Sustainability%20Mission%20-%20Conclave%2C%20Mr%20Joshi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20protect%20nature.%20India%20treats%20nature%20as%20God.%20Reforms%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20government%20in%20the%20renewable%20energy%20sector%20have%20put%20India%20very%20high%20in%20the%20world%20on%20several%20green%20energy%20barometers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20installed%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20has%20surged%20by%20an%20impressive%20165%20per%20cent%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20rising%20from%2075.52%20GW%20to%20over%20203%20GW%2C%20Mr%20Joshi%20said.%20This%20surge%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20increase%20in%20renewable%20energy%20generation%2C%20which%20grew%20from%20193.5%20billion%20units%20(BU)%20to%20360%20BU%20between%202013%20and%202024%20-%20an%2086%20per%20cent%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20best%20aspect%20of%20the%20renewable%20energy%20growth%20story%20is%20that%20the%20solution%20is%20being%20provided%20not%20just%20by%20the%20government%20but%20also%20by%20the%20business%20community%2C%20consumers%20and%20common%20citizens.%20The%20results%20are%20starting%20to%20show%20remarkable%20change%20-%20a%20165%25%20growth%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Joshi%20said%20that%20India's%20solar%20power%20costs%20are%20among%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20world%2C%20due%20in%20part%20to%20the%20country's%20abundant%20sunny%20days%2C%20which%20contribute%20to%20the%20rapid%20expansion%20of%20the%20solar%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20not%20just%20another%20player%20but%20we%20are%20leading%20right%20now.%20Between%202004%20to%202014%2C%20the%20total%20expenditure%20on%20renewable%20energy%20was%20Rs%206%2C091%20crore.%20Only%20this%20year's%20budget%20on%20renewable%20energy%20is%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore.%20In%20the%20last%20ten%20years%2C%20we%20have%20spent%20Rs%2037%2C000%20crore%20on%20renewable%20energy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20central%20challenges%20to%20decarbonising%20India's%20electricity%20grid%2C%20according%20to%20Mr%20Joshi%2C%20is%20meeting%20incremental%20energy%20demand%20entirely%20through%20non-fossil%20fuel%20sources.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20the%20development%20of%20large-scale%20energy%20storage%20systems%20is%20critical.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20revealed%20that%20a%20new%20policy%20to%20promote%20pumped%20storage%20projects%20(PSPs)%20is%20in%20the%20pipeline.%20These%20projects%20aim%20to%20store%20surplus%20electricity%20and%20integrate%20renewable%20energy%20sources%20more%20efficiently%20into%20the%20national%20grid%2C%20thereby%20accelerating%20India's%20shift%20toward%20a%20low-carbon%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Joshi%20said%20under%20PM%20Modi's%20leadership%2C%20not%20only%20has%20India%20increased%20its%20energy%20output%2C%20but%20the%20cost%20of%20solar%20energy%20has%20also%20significantly%20decreased.%20Solar%20power%20tariffs%20for%20grid-connected%20plants%20dropped%20by%2076%25%20over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20from%20Rs%2010.95%20per%20unit%20in%202010-11%20to%20Rs%202.60%20per%20unit%20in%202023-24%2C%20making%20solar%20energy%20more%20accessible%20and%20cost-effective%20for%20consumers%20and%20businesses%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725606720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F4q5pai4g_pralhad-joshi-_625x300_06_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmassive-boost-in-sustainable-energy-spending-by-government-pralhad-joshi-6503194%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pralhad%20Joshi%2C%20Minister%20of%20New%20and%20Renewable%20Energy%2C%20today%20said%20that%20the%20Centre%20has%20spent%20significantly%20on%20sustainable%20energy%20for%20a%20greener%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmassive-boost-in-sustainable-energy-spending-by-government-pralhad-joshi-6503194%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Impartial%20force'%20must%20be%20deployed%20to%20Sudan%3A%20UN%20experts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725606363000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113117950%2Cimgsize-1393920.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fimpartial-force-must-be-deployed-to-sudan-un-experts%2Farticleshow%2F113117730.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113117730.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EUN%20experts%20have%20urged%20for%20an%20independent%20force%20to%20protect%20millions%20of%20civilians%20displaced%20by%20Sudan's%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20the%20national%20army%20and%20paramilitary%20forces.%20A%20fact-finding%20mission%20uncovered%20severe%20rights%20violations%2C%20including%20airstrikes%20on%20civilian%20targets%20and%20sexual%20violence%2C%20which%20may%20amount%20to%20war%20crimes.%20Immediate%20action%20is%20needed%20to%20safeguard%20affected%20populations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagemen