lls%20Tells%20NDTV...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPolls%C2%A0prophet%20Allan%20Lichtman%2C%20often%C2%A0called%C2%A0the%20%26quot%3BNostradamus%20of%20US%20presidential%20elections%26quot%3B%2C%20has%20predicted%20that%20Democratic%20presidential%20nominee%20Kamala%20Harris%20will%20win%20the%20race%20to%20the%20White%20House%20this%20year.%20In%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Litchman%2C%20who%20has%C2%A0correctly%20predicted%C2%A0nine%20out%20of%C2%A010%C2%A0election%C2%A0results%2C%20said%20that%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20will%20beat%20Republican%20Presidential%20nominee%20Donald%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20accurately%20predict%20who%20will%20occupy%20the%20Oval%20Office%2C%20Mr%20Lichtman%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnostradamus-of-us-presidential-polls-makes-his-prediction-for-2024-5569902%5C%22%3Edesigned%20what%20he%20calls%20%26quot%3B13%20keys%20to%20the%20White%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20groundbreaking%20method%20that%20revolutionized%20election%20forecasting.%20The%20keys%2C%20comprising%20a%20series%20of%20true%20or%20false%20questions%2C%20assess%20various%20factors%20such%20as%20party%20mandate%2C%20contest%2C%20incumbency%2C%20third%20party%2C%20short-term%20economy%2C%20long-term%20economy%2C%20foreign%20success%2C%20social%20unrest%2C%20incumbent%20charisma%20and%20challenger%20charisma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lichtman%20explained%20that%20if%20six%20or%20more%20keys%20go%20against%20the%20White%20House%20party%2C%20they%20are%20predicted%20losers%2C%20or%20else%20they%20are%20predicted%20winners.%20While%20Kamala%20Harris%20has%20secured%20eight%20of%20Mr%20Litchman's%20keys%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Trump%20only%20has%20three%20of%20his%20keys.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20lost%20the%20mandate%20key%2C%20which%20is%20based%20on%20losses%20in%20US%20house%20election.%20They%20have%20obviously%20lost%20the%20incumbency%20key%20with%20Biden%20not%20running.%20But%20with%20the%20party%20uniting%20around%20Harris%2C%20the%20avoided%20the%20loss%20of%20the%20contest%20key.%20Finally%2C%20the%20third%20key%20that%20they%20lost%20was%20incumbent%20charisma%20key%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained%2C%20adding%20that%20Democrats%20will%20hold%20on%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EALSO%20READ%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnostradamus-of-us-presidential-polls-makes-his-prediction-for-2024-5569902%5C%22%3E'Nostradamus'%20Of%20US%20Presidential%20Polls%20Makes%20His%20Prediction%20For%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EForeign%20Policy%20Success%2C%20Failures%20Undecided%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Litchman%2C%20who%20has%20successfully%20predicted%20election%20outcomes%20since%201984%2C%20said%20foreign%20policy%20failure%20and%20success%20remain%20undecided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20other%20two%20keys%20that%20are%20shaky%20are%20the%20two%20foreign%20policy%20keys%2C%20he%20explains%2C%20because%20the%20wars%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20Ukraine%20are%20so%20fluid.%20I%20think%20those%20keys%20will%20split%20and%20Harris%20will%20be%20down%204%20keys.%20But%20even%20if%20they%20both%20flip%20negative%2C%20this%20means%20Harris%20is%20down%20only%205%20keys%2C%20still%20one%20key%20short%20of%20defeat.%20All%20other%20keys%20are%20locked%20in%20her%20favour%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20areas%20of%20uncertainty%2C%20the%20US%20historian%20said%20%26quot%3BTwo%20areas%20of%20uncertainty%20are%20two%20foreign%20policy%20keys-%20foreign%20military%20success%20and%20failure.%20We%20don't%20know%20exactly%20what%20could%20happen%20in%20Ukraine%20or%20Middle%20East.%20But%20they%20won't%20affect%20my%20prediction%20that%20Kamala%20Harris%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20next%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20These%20two%20keys%20are%20not%20enough%20to%20predict%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20could%20regain%20the%20White%20House.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Short-Term%2C%20Long-Term%20Economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20two%20economic%20keys%20are%20statistical%20and%20they%20are%20very%20specifically%20defined.%20The%20short-term%20economy%20key%20says%20there%20is%20no%20recession%20in%20the%20election%20year.%20You%20can't%20just%20have%20recession%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20it%20takes%20much%20longer%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20long%20term%20economy%20key%20asks%20whether%20the%20per%20capita%20growth%20on%20the%20current%20term%20is%20equal%20to%20the%20average%20of%20previous%20two%20terms.%20%C2%A0And%20per%20capita%20growth%20under%20Biden%20is%20double%20or%20more%20that%20that%20of%20the%20average%20of%20previous%20two%20terms%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20Republicans%20could%20do%20anything%20to%20fare%20better%2C%20the%20election%20forecaster%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20actually%20nothing%20they%20can%20do.%20That's%20the%20whole%20point%20of%20the%20keys.%20It%20is%20fundamentally%20different%20that%20all%20of%20the%20conventional%20wisdoms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lichtman's%20predictive%20prowess%20faced%20its%20most%20significant%20test%20in%20the%20tumultuous%202000%20election%20between%20Al%20Gore%20and%20George%20W%20Bush.%20While%20he%20forecasted%20a%20victory%20for%20Gore%2C%20the%20controversial%20outcome%20cast%20a%20shadow%20over%20his%20prediction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EALSO%20READ%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffactbox-what-new-proposals-did-trump-make-during-his-economic-speech-6501352%5C%22%3EFactbox%3A%20What%20New%20Proposals%20Did%20Trump%20Make%20During%20His%20Economic%20Speech%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725606060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F