s%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725600762000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113114602%2Cimgsize-17052.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fntr-jrs-devara-jumps-by-nearly-200-in-4-days-for-its-usa-premiere-shows%2Farticleshow%2F113114665.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113114665.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAdvance%20sales%20for%20NTR%20Jr%E2%80%99s%20Devara%20began%20in%20late%20August%20and%20quickly%20surpassed%20Rs%201%20crore.%20Releasing%20on%20September%2027%2C%20it%20has%20expanded%20to%20207%20locations%20with%20nearly%20600%20shows%20and%20earned%20over%20Rs%203.45%20crore%20for%20its%20premiere%20shows.%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan%20debuts%20in%20Telugu%20cinema%20as%20the%20antagonist%2C%20alongside%20Janhvi%20Kapoor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fntr-jrs-devara-jumps-by-nearly-200-in-4-days-for-its-usa-premiere-shows%2Farticleshow%2F113114665.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UPI%20Circle%20Launched%3A%20What%20Is%20It%2C%20How%20Does%20It%20Work%20And%20Other%20Details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%20has%20launched%20a%20new%20feature%20called%20%26quot%3BUPI%20Circle%26quot%3B%2C%20aimed%20at%20enhancing%20digital%20payment%20accessibility.%20This%20new%20feature%20allows%20primary%20users%20to%20add%20family%20members%20and%20friends%20as%20secondary%20users%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20make%20transactions%20using%20the%20primary%20user's%20bank%20account%2C%20all%20within%20pre-set%20limits.%20It%20is%20designed%20to%20extend%20the%20convenience%20of%20UPI%20transactions%20to%20those%20who%20may%20not%20have%20their%20own%20bank%20accounts%20or%20are%20hesitant%20about%20using%20digital%20payments.%20As%20per%20NPCI%2C%20the%20feature%20is%20aimed%20at%20empowering%20secondary%20users%20who%20might%20be%20financially%20dependent%20to%20access%20UPI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUPI%20Circle%20features%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2C%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npci.org.in%2Fwhat-we-do%2Fupi-circle%2Fproduct-overview%5C%22%3Epress%20note%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20NPCI%20detailed%20the%20features%20of%20%26quot%3BUPI%20Circle%26quot%3B.%20As%20per%20the%20agency%2C%20primary%20users%20can%20now%20delegate%20payment%20authorisation%20to%20secondary%20users%2C%20such%20as%20family%20members%20or%20employees%2C%20who%20can%20then%20perform%20transactions%20directly%20from%20the%20primary%20user's%20account.%20This%20feature%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20particularly%20beneficial%20for%20parents%20providing%20allowances%20to%20children%2C%20senior%20citizens%20who%20are%20cautious%20about%20conducting%20digital%20transactions%2C%20and%20business%20owners%20who%20need%20to%20manage%20petty%20cash%20for%20their%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20feature%20does%20come%20with%20layers%20of%20intervention%20and%20security%20measures.%20Once%20added%2C%20primary%20users%20will%20have%20the%20option%20to%20set%20spending%20limits%20or%20require%20approval%20for%20each%20transaction.%20The%20%26quot%3BSpend%20With%20Limits%26quot%3B%20option%20allows%20secondary%20users%20to%20make%20payments%20within%20defined%20limits%20without%20needing%20further%20approval%2C%20while%20the%20%26quot%3BApprove%20Every%20Payment%26quot%3B%20option%20offers%20greater%20control%20by%20requiring%20the%20primary%20user's%20approval%20for%20each%20transaction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENPCI%20has%20set%20the%20maximum%20monthly%20limit%20at%20Rs%2015%2C000%20where%20a%20single%20transaction%20cannot%20exceed%20Rs%205%2C000.%20Also%2C%20for%20the%20first%2024%20hours%2C%20the%20secondary%20user%20will%20have%20a%20limit%20of%20Rs%205%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20agency%2C%20the%20primary%20user%20will%20have%20the%20option%20to%20monitor%20the%20activity%20of%20the%20secondary%20users%20on%20the%20app.%20A%20primary%20user%20can%20set%20different%20maximum%20limits%20(under%20Rs%2015%2C000)%20for%20different%20secondary%20users.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbout%206%25%20of%20UPI%20users%20make%20a%20large%20number%20of%20transactions%2C%20mainly%20because%20they%20also%20make%20transactions%20on%20behalf%20of%20others.%20This%20feature%20will%20allow%20the%20primary%20user%20to%20have%20the%20same%20control%20while%20offering%20more%20convenience%20while%20making%20delegated%20payments%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20NPCI%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20set%20up%20UPI%20Circle%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGo%20to%20UPI%20Circle%20Menu%3A%20Tap%20%26quot%3BAdd%20Family%20or%20Friends%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEnter%20a%20secondary%20UPI%20ID%2C%20scan%20their%20UPI%20QR%20code%2C%20or%20search%20your%20phone%20contacts%20to%20add%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESet%20Permissions%3A%20Choose%20between%20%26quot%3BSpend%20With%20Limits%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BApprove%20Every%20Payment%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESecondary%20user%20will%20receive%20a%20notification%20to%20accept%20the%20request%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOnce%20accepted%2C%20secondary%20users%20can%20start%20making%20payments%20using%20the%20primary%20user's%20UPI%20account%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20a%20primary%20user%20can%20add%20up%20to%20five%20secondary%20users%2C%20however%2C%20a%20secondary%20user%20can%20only%20accept%20a%20single%20primary%20user.%20The%20primary%20user%20can%20also%20revoke%20access%20to%20the%20secondary%20user%20at%20any%20given%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725600240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-08%2Ftbld3cbg_upi-generic_625x300_02_August_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fupi-circle-launched-what-is-it-how-does-it-work-and-other-details-6502572%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(NPCI)%20has%20launched%20a%20new%20feature%20called%20%26quot%3BUPI%20Circle%26quot%3B%2C%20aimed%20at%20enhancing%20digital%20payment%20accessibility.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fupi-circle-launched-what-is-it-how-does-it-work-and-other-details-6502572%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vivo%20T3%20Ultra%20launching%20soon%20in%20India%3A%20Check%20specifications%2C%20price%20details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725600150000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-09%2F06%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1725599519-0087.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fvivo-t3-ultra-launching-soon-in-india-check-specifications-price-details-124090600212_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vivo%20T3%20Ultra%20smartphone%20will%20be%20priced%20under%20Rs%2033%2C000%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20the%20product%20listing%20page%20on%20e-commerce%20platform%20Flipkart%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fvivo-t3-ultra-launching-soon-in-india-check-specifications-price-details-124090600212_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fvivo-t3-ultra-launching-soon-in-india-check-specifications-price