0Google%20Maps.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20worst%20Taco%20Bell%20in%20the%20US%20is%20in%20Florida%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20analysis%20from%20the%20business%20magazine%20Fast%20Company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20August%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fastcompany.com%2F91174154%2Ftaco-bell-best-worst-pacifica-california-reviews-franchise%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Fast%20Company%20analyzed%20Taco%20Bell%20locations%20around%20the%20country%20to%20determine%20which%20were%20the%20best%20and%20worst%20outlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20assessing%20all%20outlets%20that%20had%20more%20than%2050%20reviews%20on%20Google%20Maps%2C%20Fast%20Company%20awarded%20the%20bottom%20spot%20to%20an%20outlet%20in%20Deltona%2C%20a%20city%20in%20northeast%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outlet%2C%20which%20was%20reviewed%20112%20times%20as%20of%20press%20time%2C%20had%201.8%20stars%20out%20of%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fast%20Company%20report%20picked%20out%20the%20review%20that%20it%20thought%20represented%20the%201519%20Saxon%20Boulevard%20outlet%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Burritos%20looked%20a%20mess%2C%20had%20missing%20ingredients%20i'm%20sure%2C%20and%20my%20supreme%20chalupa%20was%20actually%20missing%20tomato%20and%20cheese%20so%20you%20know%202%2F4%20ingredients%20missing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20review%20read%2C%20per%20the%20report%20by%20Fast%20Company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTake%20a%20gamble%20if%20you%20wish%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20review%20added%2C%20per%20the%20media%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20reviews%20of%20the%20outlet%20on%20Google%20Maps%20complained%20about%20long%20waiting%20times%2C%20missing%20ingredients%2C%20and%20insufficient%20portions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outlet%20did%20not%20return%20a%20phone%20call%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20Taco%20Bell%20that%20clinched%20the%20top%20spot%20was%20located%20in%20Pacifica%2C%20California.%20The%20outlet%2C%20located%20on%20the%20seafront%20near%20San%20Jose%2C%20had%20a%20rating%20of%204.4%20stars%20out%20of%20five%2C%20with%20over%203%2C470%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20best%20Taco%20Bell%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20review%20for%20the%20outlet%20on%20Google%20Maps%20read.%20%26quot%3BThe%20food%20and%20view%20are%20so%20worth%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%207%2C775%20Taco%20Bell%20outlets%20in%20the%20US%2C%20per%20the%20chain's%20list%20at%20press%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Fast%20Company's%20methodology%2C%20all%20the%20chain's%20outlets%20with%20at%20least%2050%20reviews%20on%20Google%20Maps%20were%20evaluated%20in%20its%20analysis.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFast%20Company%20compiled%20its%20data%20on%20the%20chains'%20restaurants%20up%20to%20July%2030%2C%202024.%20Each%20outlet%20was%20given%20a%20weighted%20score%2C%20accounting%20for%20the%20average%20review%20score%20customers%20gave%20the%20outlet%2C%20and%20factoring%20in%20the%20number%20of%20reviews%20%3Cspan%3Ethe%20outlet%20received.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Taco%20Bell%2C%20Fast%20Company%20also%20analyzed%20rankings%20for%20chains%20including%20McDonald's%2C%20KFC%2C%20and%20Burger%20King.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20found%20that%20McDonald's%20best%20and%20worst%20outlets%20were%20both%20located%20in%20southern%20Texas.%20Its%20best%20outlet%2C%202130%20Main%20Street%20in%20Eagle%20Pass%2C%20Texas%2C%20had%20a%20rating%20of%204.3%20and%20over%201%2C900%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20worst%20outlet%20was%20in%20San%20Antonio%2C%20and%20had%20a%20rating%20of%203.0%20and%20139%20reviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerica's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fastcompany.com%2F91174132%2Fkfc-best-worst-franchise-reviews-lax%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20hated%20KFC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20at%20LAX%2C%20with%20a%201.5-star%20review%2C%20Fast%20Company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fastcomp