ng%20that%20he%20didn't%20like%20that%20school%20shootings%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bfact%20of%20life%26quot%3B%20during%20a%20Thursday%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVance's%20comments%20come%20one%20day%20after%20a%2014-year-old%20suspect%20opened%20fire%20at%20a%20Georgia%20high%20school%20in%20a%20rampage%20that%20left%20two%20teachers%20and%20two%20students%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20these%20psychos%20are%20going%20to%20go%20after%20our%20kids%2C%20we've%20got%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Vance%20said%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Associated%20Press.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20to%20like%20the%20reality%20that%20we%20live%20in%2C%20but%20it%20is%20the%20reality%20we%20live%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20senator%20from%20Ohio%20continued%2C%20saying%20he%20didn't%20%26quot%3Blike%26quot%3B%20that%20such%20shootings%20are%20%26quot%3Ba%20fact%20of%20life%26quot%3B%20but%20said%20American%20schools%20are%20%26quot%3Bsoft%20targets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20to%20bolster%20security%2C%20so%20if%20a%20psycho%20wants%20to%20walk%20through%20the%20front%20door%20and%20kill%20a%20bunch%20of%20children%2C%20they're%20not%20able%2C%26quot%3B%20Vance%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris'%20campaign%20quickly%20jumped%20on%20Vance's%20comments%2C%20with%20her%20campaign%20posting%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FKamalaHQ%2Fstatus%2F1831861963187519518%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Vance's%20rally%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Vance%20did%20not%20specifically%20respond%20to%20a%20question%20about%20his%20comments%20that%20school%20shootings%20are%20a%20part%20of%20America's%20%26quot%3Breality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKamala%20Harris%20has%20called%20for%20all%20police%20officers%20to%20be%20removed%20from%20schools%2C%20putting%20children%20all%20over%20America%20at%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20Vance's%20spokesperson%20said%20