.com%2Ftelegram-ceo-pavel-durov-charges-questions-free-speech-censorship-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreliminary%20charges%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20days%20later%2C%20on%20August%2028.%20Durov%20was%20accused%20of%20being%20complicit%20in%20the%20distribution%20of%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20material%20and%20drug%20trafficking%20on%20Telegram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDurov%2C%20who%20obtained%20French%20citizenship%20in%202021%2C%20has%20since%20been%20released%20from%20custody%20though%20he%20is%20not%20allowed%20to%20leave%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20country%20is%20unhappy%20with%20an%20internet%20service%2C%20the%20established%20practice%20is%20to%20start%20a%20legal%20action%20against%20the%20service%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20Durov%20wrote%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsing%20laws%20from%20the%20pre-smartphone%20era%20to%20charge%20a%20CEO%20with%20crimes%20committed%20by%20third%20parties%20on%20the%20platform%20he%20manages%20is%20a%20misguided%20approach.%20Building%20technology%20is%20hard%20enough%20as%20it%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrench%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20said%20on%20August%2026%20that%20Durov's%20arrest%20is%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3Ein%20no%20way%20a%20political%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EI%20have%20seen%20false%20information%20regarding%20France%20following%20the%20arrest%20of%20Pavel%20Durov.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3EFrance%20is%20deeply%20committed%20to%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20communication%2C%20to%20innovation%2C%20and%20to%20the%20spirit%20of%20entrepreneurship.%20It%20will%20remain%20so.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3EIn%20a%20state%20governed%20by%20the%20rule%20of%20law%2C%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%