1%20and%20inspire%20a%20new%20generation%20of%20female%20racers.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20female%20athlete%2C%20I%20am%20particularly%20motivated%20to%20challenge%20the%20norms%20and%20make%20a%20significant%20impact%20in%20a%20field%20that%20has%20historically%20been%20male-dominated%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fmagazines%2Fpanache%2Fmeet-25-yr-old-salva-marjan-keralas-first-woman-to-join-formula-1-racing-academy%2Farticleshow%2F112728519.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeet%2025-yr-old%20Salva%20Marjan%2C%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20first%20woman%20set%20to%20join%20Formula%201%20racing%20academy%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20The%20Economic%20Times%2C%20Published%20on%2023%20August%202024%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkeralakaumudi.com%2Fen%2Fnews%2Fnews.php%3Fid%3D1364154%26u%3Dbraking-stereotypes-salva-marjan%25E2%2580%2599s-race-to-become-kerala%25E2%2580%2599s-first-formula-one-racer-1364154%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESalva%20Marjan%E2%80%99s%20race%20to%20become%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20first%20Formula%20One%20racer%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20Kaumudi%20Online%2C%20Published%20on%2013%20August%202024%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsalvamarjan.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAbout%20Salva%20Marjan%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20by%20salvamarjan.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724852716000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D363299%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hailing%20from%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Kerala%2C%2025-year-old%20Salva%20Marjan%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20making%20hist